# Hunting

| Animal     | Success |
|------------|---------|
| House cat  | 32%     |
| Lion       | 25%     |
| Wolf       | 14%     |

A house cat is a more efficient predator than a lion. This is the single most counter-intuitive fact about domestic cats and it deserves to be on every cat deck ever made.

